00:39:34,950 --> 00:39:49,520
because philosophy, as we know it, emerged in Europe and if we apply the same notion to Chinese thought, that Chinese thought is automatically in a disadvantage, and so on and so on.

313
00:39:50,130 --> 00:39:58,204
