322
00:41:13,310 --> 00:41:15,988
The same goes for market commodities and so on.

323
00:41:16,410 --> 00:41:20,369
So universality is a way of life, as it were.

324
00:41:20,670 --> 00:41:23,906
It's a mode of our immediate experience.

