345
00:44:06,630 --> 00:44:13,128
she was, England was the unconscious tool of history in bringing about the revolution.

346
00:44:13,430 --> 00:44:15,948
Now this is the Marx usually attacked.

347
00:44:17,951 --> 00:44:23,124
One should not dismiss here the talk of the unconscious tool of history.

348
00:44:24,171 --> 00:44:33,128
Marx is not a naive teleologist, claiming oh, the British brutal exploitation of India was a tool of some higher historical reason

349
00:44:33,470 --> 00:44:37,843
which made it an instrument of future progress and so on and so on.

350
00:44:38,550 --> 00:44:44,188
All Marx claims is that the British colonization of India

351
00:44:44,830 --> 00:44:57,582
unintendedly created conditions for the double liberation of India from the constraints of its own traditions as well as from colonization itself.

352
00:44:59,410 --> 00:45:02,447
