00:46:10,330 --> 00:46:16,366
a detailed justification of caste system with detailed descriptions what were to do.

362
00:46:17,130 --> 00:46:24,369
You know, I learned with surprise for my Indian friends that in 17th century at least this book was half forgotten.

363
00:46:24,690 --> 00:46:26,867
It was just lost in different transcriptions.

364
00:46:27,271 --> 00:46:34,425
It is in the earlier 19th century that the British colonizers reestablished, resuscitated this book.

365
00:46:35,030 --> 00:46:47,727
